description:
Remove shadow, spot and staple hole; correct and enhance documents.

Jidu Document Clear is a scan cleaning and preprocessing software developed by the Weizhi team of Weilonghui Technology Co., Ltd., which is easy to use and can produce good results. With machine learning algorithms, it can quickly preprocess all kinds of problematic files to archive or convert them into editable files or searchable double-layer PDF/A, OFD, etc.
